Package com.lonepulse.robozombie.processor

Contains the contracts and abstract implementations which provide the infrastructure to process requests and responses using the meta-data on an endpoint.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Processor<RESULT,FAILURE extends Throwable> This contract defines a strategy which accepts data, acts on them (based on predefined instructions) and returns a result.
 

Class Summary
AbstractProcessorChain<LINK_RESULT,LINK_FAILURE extends Throwable> This contract defines the services for a chain of sequentially executed ProcessorChainLinks.
ProcessorChainFactory<RESULT,FAILURE extends Throwable> This is a concrete implementation of AbstractGenericFactory which creates a processor chain using the given array of Processors which are wrapped in ProcessorChainLinks and linked together.
ProcessorChainLink<RESULT,FAILURE extends Throwable> Represents a single link in a processor chain.
 

Enum Summary
Processors This enum aggregates all thread-safe processor-chains and exposes the services common to each chain and may even offer services which encompass all the chains as a whole.
